<L>__{exterior quadrangle day}
<B>__{full shot}
<A>__{the jap strafing attack is continuing. their planes are making a figure 8 in the sky. silhouettes of men on the roof can b e seen. friday clark is blowing his cavalry charge. in b.g. men of the loading detail are scurrying around. lieutenant ross runs into shot. camera pans him across the quadrangle toward the barracks.}
<B>__{medium shot near barracks}
